{
  "stem": "12674.7",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they were only paying $50 or $60 at that time, for a bookkeeper.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was making $125.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a guy that worked in an advertising agency on Madison Avenue, they had an article in 'The Post.' He was making $111 a week.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So my husband-- I met-- I met my husband.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we-- we-- we-- he was from Vienna too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we got married.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His-- his-- his name is Bert, Bert Manning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was from Vienna too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He came to this-- he came to this country in-- in-- 1939.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was in the American Army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was in CID at the end of the war, in-- in-- in-- in the army.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was interrogating German prisoners and things like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then he came back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he didn't have a profession, because before the war he had been working as a sheet metal worker.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one day he fell.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was saved by this much, but not-- he fell off of a-- a scaffolding-- from not smashing his head into-- into a concrete sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he didn't want to go back to that kind of business, even though it was well-paying job.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we decided-- we decided I was going to go to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was making enough money to carry us both.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was going to go to school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he took-- he went for engineering.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he did-- he did it in 23 months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He went-- went 11-- he went for 11 months, and then another year later.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He took a month off in between.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he took the whole course in 23 months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was working, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Like, he was taking double and triple things, everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he had been in the engineers before he went into the intelligence.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
